title: Arizona 30th District State Senate Results: Robert Meza Wins
title_page: Arizona 30th District State Senate Results: Robert Meza Wins – Election Results 2016 – The New York Times
maintext:
State Senator Robert Meza won the 30th District State Senate race in Arizona on Tuesday. Meza is up by 30 points with all precincts reporting.
